OL,3,CEnvironmental group challenges
OL,4,CShropshire Council over major poultry
OL,5,Cunits
OL,7,FA legal challenge has been brought
OL,8,Fagainst Shropshire Council's decision
OL,9,Fto approve the building of a
OL,10,Fcollection of large poultry units.
OL,12,FThe council approved the plans in May
OL,13,Fthis year.
OL,15,FThey include four poultry rearing
OL,16,Fbuildings, each over 100 metres long,
OL,17,Fand a biomass store with boilers at
OL,18,FNorth Farm, Felton Butler, and
OL,19,FMontford Bridge in Shropshire.
