OL,7,FThe unit would house 230,000 birds,
OL,8,Fjust 400 metres from an existing
OL,9,Fpoultry site which is believed to
OL,10,Fhouse nearly half a million birds.
OL,12,FEnvironmental campaign group River
OL,13,FAction made the challenge over fears
OL,14,Fof pollution to the River Severn, with
OL,15,Fthe River Wye already having issues
OL,16,Fwith agricultural pollution.
