OL,7,FThey say the Wye catchment area has
OL,8,Fbeen devastated by the failure to
OL,9,Fenforce anti-pollution regulations,
OL,10,Fand says it is determined to help
OL,11,Fprevent similar ecological damage to
OL,12,Fthe neighbouring catchment of the
OL,13,FRiver Severn.
OL,15,FRicardo Gama from Leigh Day solicitors
OL,16,Fsaid: "What your viewers will probably
OL,17,Fknow about is the rapid decline of the
OL,18,FRiver Wye in recent years.
OL,20,F"And the primary reason for that, we
OL,21,Fknow is agricultural pollution".
