OL,7,FShropshire Council says the planning
OL,8,Fdecision was made 'having taken full
OL,9,Faccount of the likely environmental
OL,10,Fimpacts'.
OL,12,FThe company behind the plans, LJ Cooke
OL,13,F& Son, said they had no comment and
OL,14,Fthat the issue is between River Action
OL,15,Fand Shropshire Council.
